descriptionHtml:
This is just a simple repacking of the Elven mod armor by xwellenx.

[b][u][color=#ffff00]I've merged the winter, autumn and spring armors into one ESP file, cleaned the form ID errors as well.[/color][/u][/b]

SEE THE ORIGINAL MOD PAGE HERE:
[b][u][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/7300/?]Elven armor and weapon retex and standalone by Wellan [/url]

[/u][/b]I've basically merged, cleaned and edited one or two small parts that were bugging me.  This is only in standalone mode, gives you the 3 armor sets to use in game.

I got permission from Wellen to upload this version, hope you enjoy this.

Enjoy.

[color=#ffff00][b]LEGAL
SPEAK TO XWELLENX if you want to use this or his original mod.
